    "name": "MapProjectionAgent",
    "description": "This agent determines an appropriate coordinate reference system for a spatial task based on the user request and the dataset context. It evaluates candidate CRS options and applies the selected transformation to a single vector dataset. It is intended for reprojection tasks where CRS choice affects spatial accuracy and analysis quality.",
